  "prompt": "Can I make a voice call from my iPad using Jio SIM?",
  "response": "Yes, you can make voice calls from an iPad with a Jio SIM, but there are a few requirements and methods:\n\n1. iPad with Cellular Data:\n- Your iPad must have cellular data capability\n- You need a Jio 4G SIM inserted in the iPad\n- The iPad must support voice over LTE (VoLTE)\n\n2. Calling Methods:\n- Use Jio apps like MyJio for calling\n- Use VoIP apps like WhatsApp, Skype, or FaceTime\n- Use Jio Voice calling feature through their network\n\n3. Additional Considerations:\n- Ensure your iPad model supports VoLTE\n- Check Jio network coverage in your area\n- Verify your Jio SIM is activated for voice calls\n\nRecommendation: Check with Jio customer support for specific compatibility and activation details for your specific iPad model.",
